Now, this Lakshmi

00:15:51.200 --> 00:15:52.200
came out of

00:15:52.560 --> 00:15:53.840
the great churning

00:15:54.360 --> 00:15:55.720
called as Amrutmanthan,

00:15:55.960 --> 00:15:58.320
for which I'll give you another lecture some other time.

00:16:01.200 --> 00:16:02.560
But

00:16:07.400 --> 00:16:08.400
this

00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:12.880
Lakshmi that came out of

00:16:13.760 --> 00:16:15.960
the churning

00:16:16.960 --> 00:16:17.960
represents

00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:22.320
our seeking into our own well-being.

00:16:23.120 --> 00:16:24.120
So, first of all,

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:26.400
we have basic

00:16:26.920 --> 00:16:28.240
seekings, like food.

00:16:29.120 --> 00:16:31.880
In the animal stage we seek food.

00:16:31.960 --> 00:16:33.760
And, with that seeking only,

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:34.960
we developed

00:16:35.080 --> 00:16:36.080
into

00:16:36.640 --> 00:16:40.720
sometimes very cunning animals, sometimes very ferocious animals

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:43.360
and sometimes very timid animals.

00:16:43.560 --> 00:16:45.800
Because they could not find food,

00:16:45.960 --> 00:16:48.120
so they had to hide and slay animals.

00:16:49.200 --> 00:16:50.200
So the food

00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:52.560
was the beginning, I should say,

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:54.440
of this Lakshmi tattwa.

00:16:55.960 --> 00:16:56.960
But

00:16:57.320 --> 00:16:59.120
when She becomes actually

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:03.320
the Lakshmi, then

00:17:04.960 --> 00:17:06.200
She has a form

00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:09.960
that suggests that the Spirit of Lakshmi

00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:11.920
is

00:17:12.840 --> 00:17:15.960
for the total well-being of human beings, total well-being.

00:17:16.320 --> 00:17:18.960
Now, totality is different from

00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:23.880
partly, because in evolution, you see, you grow partly,

00:17:24.280 --> 00:17:27.360
till you reach a stage where you really achieve your

00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:28.880
total well-being.

00:17:28.960 --> 00:17:31.360
And now, you know that, without realization

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:33.080
your well-being has no meaning.

00:17:34.840 --> 00:17:36.680
So, She has

00:17:37.400 --> 00:17:39.640
arisen out of the sea,

00:17:39.920 --> 00:17:41.080
so She is

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:44.400
Miriam, you can call Her. She is Marie,

00:17:44.800 --> 00:17:49.600
She is Marie. That's why Christ's Mother's name was Mary

00:17:50.040 --> 00:17:53.800
because She came out of the sea.

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:58.560
People, I don't know if they think about it, why She was called

00:17:58.760 --> 00:18:00.800
Mary, of all the things. Why this name, Mary?

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:05.800
Now, this

00:18:08.200 --> 00:18:11.280
power which came out of the sea,

00:18:13.880 --> 00:18:14.880
because

00:18:15.080 --> 00:18:17.720
the whole thing, the seeking started in the sea, first of all,

00:18:17.920 --> 00:18:19.960
as you know. It had to be in the sea, because

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:23.000
first animals were born in the sea only.

00:18:26.640 --> 00:18:29.080
Becomes, when She comes out of the sea,

00:18:29.840 --> 00:18:30.840
becomes

00:18:32.760 --> 00:18:34.040
a Raja Lakshmi

00:18:35.160 --> 00:18:36.760
and a Gruha Lakshmi.

00:18:37.400 --> 00:18:39.000
Raja Lakshmi is the One

00:18:40.040 --> 00:18:42.320
where collectively

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:45.840
collectively you enjoy your well-being.

00:18:46.200 --> 00:18:47.680
Collectively.

00:18:48.280 --> 00:18:49.840
On the right hand side you can say.

00:18:50.320 --> 00:18:52.600
Like, we have

00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:55.920
some places which are for public usage, here,

00:18:56.560 --> 00:18:58.880
public well-being.

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:04.280
And Gruha Lakshmi is the one which is for the individual,

00:19:06.040 --> 00:19:08.320
individual well-being.

00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:11.320
So we have the essence of Lakshmi

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:14.720
and then we have,

00:19:15.720 --> 00:19:16.960
when we evolved

00:19:17.400 --> 00:19:20.000
we started having our homes, houses,

00:19:20.660 --> 00:19:23.620
our own family, our own private life, our these things.

00:19:24.320 --> 00:19:25.440
So we had,

00:19:26.120 --> 00:19:27.240
Gruha Lakshmi.

00:19:28.280 --> 00:19:31.320
And then they started having collective,

00:19:32.720 --> 00:19:35.560
like we can say, the queen represents here Raja Lakshmi.

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:37.120
A queen represents

00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:39.880
here a Raja Lakshmi of England.

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:42.200
She is a symbol of that.

00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:45.560
Our queen here is the symbol of that Raja Lakshmi.

00:19:46.280 --> 00:19:47.960
You know the word "raja" means

00:19:48.640 --> 00:19:50.560
the kingdom or you can say the

00:19:55.160 --> 00:19:56.280
the royal,

00:19:56.920 --> 00:19:58.600
royal kind of the reality.

00:19:58.960 --> 00:20:02.600
So when the Lakshmi is a regal Lakshmi, She is for collectivity.

00:20:04.440 --> 00:20:06.120
So the queen doesn't

00:20:06.640 --> 00:20:08.320
live for herself, she lives for

00:20:08.760 --> 00:20:09.960
all the collective being.

00:20:10.760 --> 00:20:13.440
In the same way, the Raja Lakshmi

00:20:13.960 --> 00:20:16.120
is the One that is for all of us.

00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:18.960
For example this place we got here,

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:20.760
it's through the blessings of Raja Lakshmi.

00:20:21.960 --> 00:20:23.120
She gave us this place.

00:20:23.600 --> 00:20:25.400
Her power gave us this place to live,

00:20:25.920 --> 00:20:27.840
because you are all Sahaja Yogis,

00:20:28.720 --> 00:20:31.280
you are the epitome of evolution,

00:20:31.360 --> 00:20:33.880
you are the highest people in the evolution,

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:35.960
you are the ones who are looked after by God,

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:37.840
you are the most important people.

00:20:38.040 --> 00:20:39.160
It's true.

00:20:39.320 --> 00:20:40.960
And you know She provided for you.

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:43.160
You should have no problem of money, you should have no problem

00:20:43.360 --> 00:20:45.640
of housing, you should have no problem of anything.

00:20:46.120 --> 00:20:49.320
So it is She, the Raja Lakshmi, who gives you all that.

00:20:50.760 --> 00:20:52.080
Then you have your wife,

00:20:52.840 --> 00:20:53.960
as Gruha Lakshmi.

00:20:56.280 --> 00:20:58.800
So we have to have a wife as Gruha Lakshmi.

00:21:00.360 --> 00:21:04.160
These two things one should understand very, very clearly

00:21:04.560 --> 00:21:05.920
because we confuse them.

00:21:06.720 --> 00:21:09.640
Wife is a Gruha Lakshmi, is the one, she is the Goddess

00:21:09.960 --> 00:21:11.440
of the household.

00:21:11.960 --> 00:21:13.600
Now she has to be the Goddess also.

00:21:13.720 --> 00:21:15.400
I mean she just doesn't become Goddess

00:21:15.600 --> 00:21:17.960
just by becoming. You have to become again.

00:21:18.760 --> 00:21:20.120
You have to become the Goddess.

00:21:20.600 --> 00:21:21.720
And the Goddess

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:23.640
of the Gruha Lakshmi

00:21:24.600 --> 00:21:25.720
is, we can say,

00:21:25.960 --> 00:21:28.360
that the deity of the gruha, of the house,

00:21:28.760 --> 00:21:29.880
is the Gruha Lakshmi.

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:33.200
Now this deity must become one with the housewife.

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:39.760
Then the blessings

00:21:40.040 --> 00:21:41.360
of the Lakshmi

00:21:41.760 --> 00:21:43.680
essence, is of well-being comes to you.

00:21:43.800 --> 00:21:45.760
If she is not the Goddess, you'll always suffer.

00:21:46.080 --> 00:21:47.280
You'll always have problems.

00:21:47.760 --> 00:21:48.880
You'll always have

00:21:49.640 --> 00:21:51.440
all kinds of untold miseries.

00:21:52.240 --> 00:21:55.320
It is Her blessings which brings you solace,

00:21:55.840 --> 00:22:00.160
peace and redemption - redemption is the word - of anything.

00:22:00.920 --> 00:22:03.080
So that's why the left Nabhi is very important

00:22:03.240 --> 00:22:06.880
as you know, and that is always bad in the present.

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:11.640
So I would say that the whole society is responsible

00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:13.000
for spoiling that,

00:22:13.720 --> 00:22:15.160
because housewife is not respected

00:22:15.680 --> 00:22:17.560
first of all. We should blame our society.

00:22:18.160 --> 00:22:19.800
Our housewives are not respected.

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:24.400
Housewife, the one who is a dedicated wife, even

00:22:24.720 --> 00:22:26.720
is placed higher than yatis.

00:22:27.640 --> 00:22:30.440
Yatis are the highest evolved,

00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:36.040
you can say, avdutas are the highest evolved

00:22:36.840 --> 00:22:37.960
seers,

00:22:38.680 --> 00:22:40.280
and a dedicated wife

00:22:41.040 --> 00:22:42.800
has got more powers

00:22:43.240 --> 00:22:45.400
than even a yati - it is said so.

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:47.440
And even Krishna was

00:22:47.920 --> 00:22:49.000
little worried about them.

00:22:49.320 --> 00:22:50.560
Everybody had to worry.

00:22:53.960 --> 00:22:55.960
So the dedicated wife, you see,

00:22:56.160 --> 00:22:58.960
the Gruha Lakshmi, is such an important thing,

00:23:00.040 --> 00:23:01.960
because she is the essence

00:23:03.920 --> 00:23:06.680
of this well-being, which is peace.

00:23:08.160 --> 00:23:10.760
I think I have so far never talked to you about peace.

00:23:13.000 --> 00:23:17.960
And peace is only achieved through the Gruha Lakshmi,

00:23:18.640 --> 00:23:19.960
through your proper

00:23:20.560 --> 00:23:22.840
adjustment of your spleen I should say.

00:23:24.640 --> 00:23:26.440
Because spleen is the giver

00:23:27.040 --> 00:23:28.160
of the

00:23:29.600 --> 00:23:31.120
blood cells. All right?

00:23:31.440 --> 00:23:34.360
It creates the nutrition for the whole body.

00:23:35.800 --> 00:23:37.000
If there is no peace

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:39.960
in that area within us,

00:23:40.880 --> 00:23:41.960
the whole

00:23:42.280 --> 00:23:45.200
system can go out because that's the nourishing

00:23:47.040 --> 00:23:49.440
center  within us, that's the nourishing center.

00:23:50.280 --> 00:23:53.000
And that center which nourishes also peace,

00:23:53.240 --> 00:23:55.160
it is the peace. You must have heard this:

00:23:55.360 --> 00:23:58.720
"Ya Devi sarva bhuteshu Shanti rupena saonsthita".

00:24:00.800 --> 00:24:02.680
The Goddess that is the Shanti

00:24:03.360 --> 00:24:05.800
which is present in every human being as peace.

00:24:07.200 --> 00:24:10.720
So this peace is only possible if the housewives

00:24:11.160 --> 00:24:12.440
realize their importance,

00:24:13.880 --> 00:24:16.320
bear it upon of themselves, are forgiving

00:24:17.080 --> 00:24:18.800
and are redeeming

00:24:20.000 --> 00:24:22.800
the family life. They have to redeem the family life.

00:24:24.320 --> 00:24:27.280
And where this gets spoiled the whole system goes out.

00:24:28.880 --> 00:24:29.960
See, America, I went

00:24:30.280 --> 00:24:32.320
and I found all of them have got left Nabhi.

00:24:33.400 --> 00:24:35.600
All right. And they are very violent.

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:38.880
Very violent, extremely violent.

00:24:39.200 --> 00:24:41.040
And what I felt that in the beginning,

00:24:41.160 --> 00:24:43.400
the society neglected the housewives,

00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:47.880
the institution of housewife which is a Goddess.

00:24:49.200 --> 00:24:51.960
And now the women cannot forgive them.

00:24:52.840 --> 00:24:56.080
Because the women cannot forgive them, you see, it has become a big

00:24:56.960 --> 00:24:57.800
struggle there.

00:24:58.240 --> 00:24:59.840
The children have become violent.

00:25:00.240 --> 00:25:02.560
I mean if the housewives are not all right

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:03.920
there will be always violence.

