the system of keeping the women in the purdah system and all those

00:25:16.800 --> 00:25:19.600
and lot of prostitution and all those ideas came

00:25:19.800 --> 00:25:22.160
through those horrible nawabs who ruled in the north.

00:25:22.800 --> 00:25:24.440
In the south it was the other way round,

00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:26.560
because they kept to the dharma and all those things

00:25:26.640 --> 00:25:28.440
and they wouldn't accept this kind of a

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:31.320
nonsensical ideas. They looked after their women.

00:25:31.560 --> 00:25:33.440
Even the people of the north sometimes say

00:25:33.800 --> 00:25:36.720
that the, I mean the south people are very

00:25:36.960 --> 00:25:39.960
sort of henpecked or whatever it is,  say Maharashtra downward.

