But the main thing is

00:26:30.960 --> 00:26:33.960
the housewife in Maharashtra is an important thing, very important.

00:26:36.440 --> 00:26:38.800
So in the house she is the,

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:41.640
she is the lady. And the lord is outside.

00:26:43.800 --> 00:26:45.560
Whatever she says, goes.

00:26:45.960 --> 00:26:48.640
But when it is the other way round, everything goes upside down.

00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:51.000
It can never be blissful.

