I mean the woman should not interfere

00:26:57.960 --> 00:27:00.680
with the husband's work in the office, should not dominate there.

00:27:00.960 --> 00:27:03.280
Like so many these women, like Chang Kai-Shek's wife did

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:05.960
and all these people did. That's not necessary.

00:27:06.840 --> 00:27:08.080
She should be a support.

00:27:08.400 --> 00:27:09.800
But in the house

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:11.960
she is the one who should be respected.

00:27:13.640 --> 00:27:15.280
She must be respected in the household,

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:18.080
otherwise there cannot be auspiciousness,

00:27:18.440 --> 00:27:19.840
there cannot be peace.

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:21.960
And peace is the gift

00:27:22.600 --> 00:27:23.720
of Gruha Lakshmi.

