Now some people may say, "Oh, it's all right,

00:27:27.600 --> 00:27:30.120
they are not having a good time, the wife is bad,

00:27:30.320 --> 00:27:32.200
but she's got money."  Money it's not Lakshmi.

00:27:34.320 --> 00:27:37.640
This confusion must be absolutely removed from your mind.

00:27:38.120 --> 00:27:40.600
And last time I explained to you what Lakshmi is.

