But you can go through again that tape, if you want to.

00:27:43.280 --> 00:27:45.040
But I'll tell you for short,

00:27:45.600 --> 00:27:47.280
that Lakshmi has got four hands.

00:27:48.960 --> 00:27:50.440
And She stands on a lotus.

00:27:51.320 --> 00:27:54.200
And She is a body with a, which is

00:27:54.880 --> 00:27:57.680
I mean, not a slim type of a body,

00:27:58.200 --> 00:28:01.280
but She has a substantial body, but She stands on a lotus.

00:28:01.440 --> 00:28:03.720
Means wherever She lives, you see,

00:28:03.960 --> 00:28:06.880
She doesn't show Her presence

00:28:07.440 --> 00:28:08.800
by staying. She is so,

00:28:09.080 --> 00:28:11.960
so beautiful that She adjusts Herself even on a lotus.

00:28:14.240 --> 00:28:16.320
She doesn't exert Her weight.

00:28:17.800 --> 00:28:21.120
Like, cheap women do, anywhere they go, they'll say,

00:28:21.320 --> 00:28:23.440
"Oh, I don't like this and I like that

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:25.320
and I would like to have this and

00:28:25.640 --> 00:28:28.040
I would like to sleep in a place like this and

00:28:28.280 --> 00:28:31.120
I, I like this type of thing."

00:28:31.880 --> 00:28:35.280
So the first quality of a woman who is a Lakshmi is adjustability.

00:28:35.960 --> 00:28:37.960
See, no one feels her when she is there

00:28:38.160 --> 00:28:40.960
nobody feels. Only thing they can feel her fragrance like a lotus.

00:28:44.160 --> 00:28:47.280
I mean that's the sign of a woman who adjusts herself.

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:50.320
She is not bothered about her own life

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:51.800
but she's bothered about others.

